	<h2>Post Graduate Internship Selection Criteria</h2>
	<ol>
		<li>Interns must have graduated from a university with a master's level degree in a mental health degree and have a temporary license in a mental health profession.</li>
		<li>Interns from CACREP approved programs will be given preference.</li>
		<li>Interns should have completed coursework in counseling theories, ethics, multicultural counseling and group counseling prior to beginning internship.</li>
		<li>Interns with play therapy training/experience will be given preference.</li>
		<li>Bilingual candidates will be given preference.</li>
		<li>Interns must pass criminal and CPS background checks.</li>
	</ol>

	<h2>Post Graduate Internship Requirements</h2>
